query:
INSERT INTO page_hreflangs (page_seo_id, lang_code, url, is_default)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
        ON CONFLICT (page_seo_id, lang_code)
        DO UPDATE
        SET url = EXCLUDED.url,
            is_default = EXCLUDED.is_default,
            updated_at = NOW()
        RETURNING id
